text: Samuel José Rodrigues Caldeira (born 30 November 1985) is a Portuguese cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Continental team . ==Major results== ;2010 : 1st 20px Overall Grande Prémio Crédito Agrícola de Costa Azul ::1st Stages 1 & 3 ;2011 : 2nd Overall Grande Prémio Crédito Agrícola de Costa Azul : 3rd Overall GP Liberty Seguros : 4th Overall Volta ao Alentejo ;2012 : 3rd Overall Volta ao Alentejo : 9th Overall Tour of Taihu Lake ;2014 : 1st Stage 5 Volta ao Alentejo ;2015 : 4th Overall Volta ao Alentejo : 6th Overall GP Liberty Seguros : 6th Clássica Loulé ;2016 : 4th Vuelta Ciclista a La Rioja : 7th Overall GP Liberty Seguros : 9th Overall Volta ao Alentejo ;2017 : 1st Stage 2 Volta a Portugal ;2019 : 1st Prologue Volta a Portugal : 7th Fyen Rundt ==References== ==External links== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese male cyclists
title: Samuel Caldeira
